### API Base URL
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000

### ========================================
### HEALTH CHECKS
### ========================================

### Health check - core-service
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### Health check with database
GET {{baseUrl}}/health/db

### ========================================
### RECIPES - GET ALL
### ========================================

### Get all recipes (empty initially)
GET {{baseUrl}}/recipes

### ========================================
### RECIPES - GET BY ID - VALID CASES
### ========================================

### Get recipe by valid ID (1)
GET {{baseUrl}}/recipes/1

### Get recipe by valid ID (2)
GET {{baseUrl}}/recipes/2

### ========================================
### RECIPES - GET BY ID - INVALID FORMAT
### ========================================

### Invalid: non-numeric ID (abc)
GET {{baseUrl}}/recipes/abc

### Invalid: decimal ID (12.4)
GET {{baseUrl}}/recipes/12.4

### Invalid: decimal with comma (12,5)
GET {{baseUrl}}/recipes/12,5

### Invalid: negative ID (-5)
GET {{baseUrl}}/recipes/-5

### Invalid: leading dot (.1)
GET {{baseUrl}}/recipes/.1

### Invalid: trailing minus (50-)
GET {{baseUrl}}/recipes/50-

### Invalid: dot only (.)
GET {{baseUrl}}/recipes/.

### Invalid: alphanumeric (40a)
GET {{baseUrl}}/recipes/40a

### ========================================
### RECIPES - GET BY ID - NON-EXISTENT
### ========================================

### Non-existent recipe (999)
GET {{baseUrl}}/recipes/999

### Non-existent recipe (1000)
GET {{baseUrl}}/recipes/1000

### ========================================
### REGRESSION TEST SUMMARY
### ========================================
### 
### Expected Results:
###
### Health checks:
###   - GET /health → 200 OK, proxied from core-service
###   - GET /health/db → 200 OK, proxied from core-service
###
### Get all recipes:
###   - GET /recipes → 200 OK, {"data":[],"count":0} (when empty)
###
### Valid IDs:
###   - GET /recipes/1 → 404 Not Found (recipe doesn't exist yet)
###   - GET /recipes/2 → 404 Not Found (recipe doesn't exist yet)
###
### Invalid formats (should all return 400):
###   - GET /recipes/abc → 400 Bad Request
###   - GET /recipes/12.4 → 400 Bad Request
###   - GET /recipes/12,5 → 400 Bad Request
###   - GET /recipes/-5 → 400 Bad Request
###   - GET /recipes/.1 → 400 Bad Request
###   - GET /recipes/50- → 400 Bad Request
###   - GET /recipes/. → 400 Bad Request
###   - GET /recipes/40a → 400 Bad Request
###
### Non-existent but valid format (should return 404):
###   - GET /recipes/999 → 404 Not Found
###   - GET /recipes/1000 → 404 Not Found
